data.text:
Professor Doug Jones A0 is a leading independent international commercial and investor-state arbitrator. Doug has chambers in Sydney and Toronto and is a door tenant at Atkin Chambers in London. In 2019, he was also appointed as an International Judge of the Singapore International Commercial Court.

Prior to his full-time practice as an arbitrator, Doug had 40 years' experience as an international transactional and disputes projects lawyer.
